Defendant in custody.
Count 1, felony bail jumping - No contest plea.  Convicted.
Sentence is withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for a period of three (3) years concurrent with probation ordered on Count 1 in 15 CF 668.
Conditions of probation:
1)   COMPAS assessment;
2)   Full-time job or work search;
3)   AODA assessment and treatment;
4)   Any other counseling deemed appropriate by the agent; 
5)   Absolute sobriety;
6)   Random drug screens the defendant will pay for;
7)   Pay restitution to L and B Pawn in the amount of $210.00;
8)   DNA sample and surcharge;
9)   Pay costs of the action; and
10) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Count 2, theft-movable property, is dismissed and read in.
Minutes.
